1. *Crno* obučen čovek je prošao pored nas. (A man dressed in black passed by us.)

2. *Crna* mačka čučala je ispred kuće. (A black cat was crouching in front of the house.)

3. *Crne* oči su joj davale misteriozni privid. (Her black eyes gave her a mysterious look.)

4. *Crnilo* je istisnuto iz štampe. (The ink was squeezed out of the press.)

5. *Crnilo* se polako isušivalo. (The ink was slowly drying.)

6. *Crnili* su se putem označavali zidovi. (The walls were being marked with ink.)